ne/nei
Homonym Number:
Word Class:exclamation
Sense Number:
Definition:interrogative, giving emphasis to a question, request, or proposal (cf. eh)
Origin:Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: usu. in Maori-English contexts  (ne, nei used in Maori like n'est-ce pas). [Ma. n&emacr. /ne:/
Citations
